 720:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
 721:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \brief
 722:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function gets Number of conversions.
 723:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
 724:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \details
 725:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function gets Number of conversions using following equation:
