1015:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
1016:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \brief
1017:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  Performs extended initialization for the CSD widget and also performs
1018:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  initialization required for a specific sensor in the widget. This function
1019:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  requires using the CapSense_CSDScanExt() function to initiate a scan.
