1649:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c ****     *   1. initializes The Compensation IDAC to zero
1650:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c ****     *   2. Enables the calibrated sensor
1651:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c ****     *   3. Performs eight iteration steps to get the target = rawLevel
