2176:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
2177:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \brief
2178:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function triggers the scanning.
2179:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
2180:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \details
2181:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  Trigger the fine initialization (scan some dummy cycles) and start sampling.
2182:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  Fine initialization for CMOD and Start scan.
2183:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  For the fine initialization and sampling, Cmod is static connected to AMUXBUS-A
2184:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  and in every conversion (one cycle of SnsClk), the sensor capacitance is charged
2185:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  from Cmod and discharged to ground using the switches in GPIO cell.
2186:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  The CSDCOMP monitors voltage on Cmod using the sense path and charges Cmod back
2187:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  to Vref using IDACs by connecting IDAC to CSDBUS-A and then the AMUXBUS-A.
2188:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
2189:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *******************************************************************************/
